      <title>中国承诺加强财政政策以刺激内需</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/china-holds-politburo-meeting-on-economy-anti-corruption-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由中共24位最高领导人组成的中国政治局誓言将加强政府财政政策以刺激内需，同时实施灵活、有针对性的货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/china-holds-politburo-meeting-on-economy-anti-corruption-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 08:07:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安盟友将瑞典的北约申办与加沙战争联系起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/turkey-s-erdogan-ally-bahceli-links-sweden-s-nato-bid-to-gaza-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安(Recep Tayyip Erdogan)的一位重要伙伴对北约的北欧扩张提出了新的质疑，此前他以以色列和巴勒斯坦之间的“永久和平”为条件支持瑞典加入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/turkey-s-erdogan-ally-bahceli-links-sweden-s-nato-bid-to-gaza-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 07:53:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特前间谍头子称巴勒斯坦问题是任何以色列协议的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/ex-saudi-spy-chief-calls-palestine-priority-for-any-israel-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯前情报负责人表示，沙特阿拉伯正在将解决巴勒斯坦问题作为与以色列接触的条件，尽管美国试图在加沙战争肆虐之际努力实现两国关系正常化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/ex-saudi-spy-chief-calls-palestine-priority-for-any-israel-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 07:24:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本致命坠机事件后，美国高级立法者寻求 V-22 鱼鹰探测器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/two-key-us-lawmakers-seek-v-22-osprey-probe-after-deadly-japan-crash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[11 月 29 日，日本海岸发生坠机事故，造成 8 名飞行员死亡，并导致该机队在全球范围内停飞，负责监督美国军事准备的两位众议院议员希望对价值 560 亿美元的 V-22 鱼鹰项目进行正式审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/two-key-us-lawmakers-seek-v-22-osprey-probe-after-deadly-japan-crash</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 05:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克里姆林宫发动文化战以在选举中团结普京选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/russia-election-2024-putin-to-campaign-as-defender-of-traditional-values</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫正在为弗拉基米尔·普京的第五次总统任期争取支持，将他宣传为俄罗斯传统价值观的捍卫者，反对“自由”西方，而乌克兰战争仍在继续，看不到任何解决方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/russia-election-2024-putin-to-campaign-as-defender-of-traditional-values</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
